Agree with @angadsalaria .
We can also make a static method which converts graphName to Traversal Source name. Something like:
public static String toTraversalSourceName(String graphName){
    return graphName + "_traversal";
}

and then use that method to convert graphName to traversalSourceName.
I.e.:
jgm.removeTraversalSource(toTraversalSourceName(graphName));

